00:22:33,500 --> 00:22:36,500
What are the xn's going to be? They're going

479
00:22:36,500 --> 00:22:39,500
to be harmonic oscillators exactly as they were before.

480
00:22:39,500 --> 00:22:41,500
They will be harmonic oscillators

481
00:22:41,500 --> 00:22:43,500
exactly as they were before.

482
00:22:43,500 --> 00:22:45,500
Oh, before I do that,

